snippet.title: Sheep Sweep - Announcement trailer PC
snippet.description: Sheep gone missing! Join Sheep Sweep, a goofy solo or coop adventure. Manipulate tools in a fully flammable world, crack unique puzzles, bypass obstacles and safely recover all the missing sheep.
